name: clara merino wool sweater
description: This is a fully fashioned polo sweater with an open neckline and dropped shoulders. It’s knit with Embrace Merino™ — extra-fine 100% merino wool yarn coveted for its natural warmth and super soft feel. We source ours from a premium Italian mill. This version features a yarn-dyed striped pattern that has been woven in, as opposed to printed on, for a more dimensional look. A Jersey stitch gives this sweater a soft drape and a smooth, flat feel.
